## Response template for delivery tasks

Use **this section order** unless the user asks for a subset:

### 1) Orchestrator

- Request analysis, task decomposition, architectural notes, risks  
- **Handoff:** explicit “Next: `@`…” with the specialist rule name and what to paste from this turn  

### 2) Senior SwiftUI Engineer  

- Plans / code changes summarized; decisions and risks  

### 3) Test Engineer  

- Tests added/changed; how to run; regression risks (**Test Engineer DoD**)  

### 4) QA Validator  

- Checklist matrix (PASS/FAIL/N/A per item); then **`PASS` or `FAIL`:**, **`RISKS:`**, **`REQUIRED FIXES:`**, **`QA SUMMARY:`**  

### 5) PR Reviewer  

- **`APPROVED`** or **`CHANGES REQUESTED`**; structured feedback bullets  

### 6) Git & Release Manager  

- Branch name; commit messages; PR title + full PR body template  

### 7) Jira / Product Ops Manager  

- Status transitions suggested; acceptance criteria updates; paste-ready comment(s); PR linkage; QA outcome text  
- **If MCP blocked:** `_Blocker:_` explanation + `_Human checklist:_` numbered steps  

### 8) Orchestrator closure

- Explicit **Orchestrator DoD** table: checklist each bullet **Done / Blocked / N/A** and why  

